gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 134, Jazz 129
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Jazz, 134-129. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander recorded 31 points, six rebounds, and six assists for the Thunder, with Jalen Williams (27 points, eight assists) and Josh Giddey (20 points, 10 rebounds) combined for 47 points in the victory. Collin Sexton tallied a season-high 31 points along with seven assists for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Thunder improve to 28-13, while the Jazz fall to 22-21.
